The '''2014 [[Asian Youth Volleyball Championship|Asian Boys' U18 Volleyball Championship]]''' was held in [[Colombo]], [[Sri Lanka]] from 5 to 13 September 2014.

{{TOCLimit|3}}

==Pools composition==
The teams are seeded based on their final ranking at the [[2012 Asian Youth Boys Volleyball Championship]].

